node.text: Happy #fungusfriday everyone! Here's a cheery basket of #chanterelles and #wildblackberries along with some #zinnias and #nightskypetunias from my garden💛💜💛💜 #cantharellus #chanterellemushrooms #chanterelleseason #wildforaging #foraging #wildfoodlove #kellogggarden #mushroomhunting #mushroomseason2021 #fungus #fungi #forestfinds #flowersofinstagram #petunias #nature #ig_naturelovers #upperpeninsulamichigan #michiganmushrooms

node.text: I feel incredibly fortunate to own/live on land that allows me to forage for edible mushrooms and fresh berries all summer💜 Picking wild blackberries is fun but painful and I have the wounds to back that statement! Ha ha🤪 #wildfood #wildfoodlove #foraging #wildforaging #michiganmushrooms #michiganmushroomhunting #pheasantbackmushroom #dryadssaddle #oystermushrooms #pleurotus #wildblackberries #mushroomseason2021 #forestfinds #nature #ig_naturelovers #fungus #fungi #thisweekoninstagram #upperpeninsulamichigan #michiganoutdoors #upnorthmichigan

node.text:
It's #tomatotuesday once again and my tomato plants are going crazy! I love getting up in the morning, heading down to the garden and harvesting a whole new batch. I also love #nasturtiums that match! This is what summer is all about😊🍅💚

node.text: Happy Sunday! This may be one of the largest #pheasantbackmushrooms I have ever found! It also seems kind of late in the season for them but this monster was growing on the same stump where I found some a couple of months ago. #cerioporussquamosus #dryadssaddle #polyporoussquamosus #polypore #polyporesofinstagram #bracketfungus #bracketfungi #mushroom #fungus #fungi #michiganmushrooms #mushroomseason2021 #michiganmushroomhunting #upperpeninsulamichigan #forestfinds #nature #ig_naturelovers

node.text: When I'm not in the woods searching for mushrooms, I'm in my other happy place--my garden! Today I'm sharing more of my fresh goodies💚 Everything is doing so well and tastes amazing. If you have ever considered growing your own food, I highly recommend it! #raisedbedgarden #raisedbedgardening #gardenlife #gardenersofinstagram #freshfood #todaysharvest #igrewthis #greenpepper #cucumber #yellowpepper #harvest #freshfromthegarden #kellogggarden #sustainablesprout #thehappygardeninglife #betterhomesandgardens #michigangardening #michigangardeningseason #green #upperpeninsulamichigan
